ls company overview of vitol holding bv snapshot people company overview vitol holding bv an energy and commodities company engages in trading refining shipping terminals and storage exploration and production marketing and power generation businesses it trades crude oil fuel oil gasoline middle distillates naphtha methanol ethanol chemicals lpg natural gas lng power coal iron ore alumina carbon emissions base oils and bitumen owns and operates refineries that distil crude oil into fuels such as gasoline diesel jet fuel and bunker oil and raw materials and owns and charters ships to deliver crude oil and oil products as well as coal bitumen chemicals and pressurized gas the company also engages in the distribution of finishe vitol holding bv an energy and commodities company engages in trading refining shipping terminals and storage exploration and production marketing and power generation businesses it trades crude oil fuel oil gasoline middle distillates naphtha methanol ethanol chemicals lpg natural gas lng power coal iron ore alumina carbon emissions base oils and bitumen owns and operates refineries that distil crude oil into fuels such as gasoline diesel jet fuel and bunker oil and raw materials and owns and charters ships to deliver crude oil and oil products as well as coal bitumen chemicals and pressurized gas the company also engages in the distribution of finished products to wholesale partners and endconsumers supplies bunker fuel for ships and jet fuel to airlines vitol holding bv was founded in  and is based in rotterdam the netherlands with additional offices worldwide it has operations in geneva houston london moscow rotterdam and singapore vitol holding bv operates as a subsidiary of vitol holding ii sa detailed description kp van der mandelelaan rotterdam   mbnetherlandsfounded in  phone     fax     wwwvitolcom key executives for vitol holding bv mr ian roper taylor chief executive officer and president age  mr miguel a loya chief executive officer