 the infrastructure upon which we rely from ships to jetties storage is subject to our due diligence processes explore trading crude oil middle distillates gasoline naphtha lpg fuel oil bitumen methanol ethanol lng natural gas power coal iron ore alumina regulatory  sds documents view all trading news visit the vitol library global oil movement the mismatch in many regions between demand and supply generates the need to move crude oil and oil products interregionally creating trading opportunities around the world the mismatch in many regions between demand and supply generates the need to move crude oil and oil products interregionally creating trading opportunities around the world oil production  demand the balance between supply and demand in energy and comodity products can be affected by many factors in the longer term demand trends are driven by population economic conditions technological advances or this diagram shows how many million barrels of oil production and demand there are per day around the world figures are based on vitol research trading  vitol who we are who we are our companies vitol aviation valt varo vivo energy viva energy australia vpi immingham vtti ventspils nafta group cockett marine oil ovh energy our business in numbers vitol foundation what we do what we do refining atpc refinery bayernoil refinery cressier refinery fujairah refinery geelong refinery trading crude oil middle distillates gasoline naphtha lpg fuel oil bitumen methanol ethanol lng natural gas power coal iron ore alumina regulatory  sds documents shipping terminals  storage downstream vitol aviation varo vtti vivo energy viva energy australia ovh energy power generation upstream working with us working with us where we work our companies vitol aviation valt varo vivo energy viva energy australia vpi immingham vtti ventspils nafta group cockett marine oil ovh energy vitol library vitol foundation foundation news responsibility news  press careers contact select country abi