and sugar essentially we trade energy we create markets for fuel products we deliver cargoes safely onspecification and ontime we provide extensive terminal and storage facilities and we engineer innovative financing structures to the benefit of our customers through the vitol foundation we are also active in charitable funding to benefit severely deprived children in asia africa latin america and cis where are we we have offices all over the world with the majority of our people located in the six key locations of geneva houston london moscow rotterdam and singapore we are active wherever our customers and the markets dictate and this inevitably gives rise to some exciting challenging and rewarding career assignments and opportunities   opportunities we are always pleased to hear from talented individuals to register your interest in a career at vitol please fill out the form below and attach a copy of your cv in english your application will be reviewed and you will be contacted should any relevant roles be available nameemail region of interest region of interestregion of interestgenevalondon  otherrotterdamafricamiddle eastsouth americanorth americaapac role applying for role applying forrole applying foradministrationcommercial analyst  trading assistantfinance  accounting  taxhuman resourcesinvestments  business developmentinformation technologylegal  claims  compliancephysical operations  schedulingorigination  marketingresearch  fundamentalsshipping  charteringtrader  brokeruniversitychoose filecandidate summary our companies our companies complement our position at the heart of the worlds energy markets and facilitate the flow of energy from into and across key markets  view companies vitol film worldwide location we understand that every market is different and that our customers and their requirements are as diverse as the world in which we live with  offices worldwide our colleagues comprise over  nationalities we understand that every market is differen